---
subject: Benvenuto in Tenant A, {{ recipient_name }}!
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head><meta charset="utf-8"></head>
<body style="font-family: sans-serif;">
  <h1 style="color:#1D4ED8;">Benvenuto, {{ recipient_name }}!</h1>
  <p>Il tuo account Tenant A è pronto.</p>
  {{- if confirmation_url }}
  <p><a href="{{ confirmation_url }}">Conferma il tuo account</a></p>
  {{- end }}
</body>
</html>
